// WORKING NAME: "AMZ" (Anti-Magic Zone)
// Class: Blood Death Knight
// Slot: passive (auto-cast on cooldown) — a band-4/5/6 unlock (in blood_death_knight's band_4_6_pool).
// Unlock: randomly at level 4/5/6.
//
// Behavior: dropped_zone — drops an "amz" zone around the character that BLOCKS projectiles
// (blocks_projectiles: true). The zone destroys any opposing-faction projectile that enters it
// (an enemy bolt aimed at the Friendly player), acting as a barrier. Per Mechanics, a projectile
// EMITTED from inside the zone is not blocked — handled by zone/systems/block.rs.
//
// amz_movespeed_rare (Phase 9.2) grants a move-speed bonus while standing inside — via the new
// `ZoneSpeedModifier` core component (core/systems/movement.rs), not this ability's own resolved
// params (it's a standing character effect keyed on zone presence, not a per-cast number).
// amz_follow_epic overrides "follow_caster" (see ability/systems/execute.rs::spawn_dropped_zone)
// to Follow the caster instead of the base Fixed drop.
(
    id: "amz",
    display_name: "AMZ",
    unlock_schedule: Band(4, 6),
    activation: AutoCast,
    behavior: "dropped_zone",
    hooks: [],
    base_params: {
        "zone_radius": 90.0,
        "zone_duration": 6.0,
        "cooldown": 12.0,
        "regen_percent_per_second": 0.0,
        "follow_caster": 0.0,
    },
    zone: Some((
        zone_type: "amz",
        anchor: Fixed,
        blocks_projectiles: true,
    )),
    talent_pool: [
        "amz_size_common",
        "amz_duration_common",
        "amz_regen_rare",
        "amz_movespeed_rare",
        "amz_follow_epic",
    ],
)
